{"title":"中国月亮","authors":["马畏安"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":10,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马畏安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昆仑山脉的峥嵘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天鹅群的俏丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚运村——北京胸襟上的珍珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华赤子爱国之心是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪滴是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老奶奶攥着人民币的拳头是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小学生手中带体温的镍币是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的月亮也是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"项羽拔山盖世的气势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞天婀娜多姿的倩影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚运城——北京前额的吉祥痣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁臂是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁碾是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗珠是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的月亮也是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像色彩斑斓的飞碟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如璀莹华丽的皇冠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚运场馆——北京颈项上的花环"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天坛的穹顶是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原子的轨迹是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从黑夜到黎明是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从除夕到元旦是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的月亮也是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天经过洗涤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳条也曾梳理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京——闪射着新时代光华的古镜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼盼的眼睛是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚运的火炬是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苹果是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸽哨是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的月亮也是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"５"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们亚洲，山是高昂的头！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头颅是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们亚洲，河像热血流！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血滴是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友谊是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的月亮也是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：中国文化报）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}